Paper: hep-th/0108024

Date: 2001-08-06

Title: Schwinger model on a half-line

Authors: Yeong-Chuan Kao and Yu-Wen Lee

Comments: 4 pages, no figure. Final version to be published on Phys. Rev. D

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D65 (2002) 067701

We study the Schwinger model on a half-line in this paper. In particular, weinvestigate the behavior of the chiral condensate near the edge of the line.The effect of the chosen boundary condition is emphasized. The extension to thefinite temperature case is straightforward in our approach.